author: Rachel England
title: Facebook's interactive COVID-19 map displays symptoms by county
description: Facebook has launched a raft of measures to help tackle the coronavirus crisis in recent weeks — its latest is a new interactive map that displays reported county-by-county COVID-19 symptoms from users across the US. The data, obtained via Facebook surveys in…
